          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The view "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Billing.vwBillingPeriods",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is a SQL Server database view that provides a simplified and structured representation of billing periods from the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Billing.BillingPeriod",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " table. It selects three columns: "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "BillingPeriod",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "BillingPeriodDescription",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", and "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Active",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ". The view is designed to present billing period data in a straightforward manner, for reporting or application consumption purposes. The absence of a check option indicates that there are no constraints on the data modifications through this view."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
